{"tid":1997141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人開始覺得限聚令其實幾好玩","createTime":"2020-05-01T12:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T05:55:13.000Z","uid":10905,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7163ae6a78367cd1f9f90f90aaebf753e893077d","tid":1997141,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:34:09.000Z","msg":"首先條限聚令對於防疫就幾有用既<br />\n問題係執行果班人鳩咁黎<br />\n諗住今次發達以為拎住張皇牌位位2000玩死你地<br />\n但一個人又話599G係商場又599G<br />\n捉2000蚊竟然要用成幾百防暴<br />\n變相玩爛左條條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果限聚令就成為左攬炒既核彈<br />\n只要日日都吹雞和你sing<br />\n班黑警就日日踩場<br />\n商場就晚晚唔洗做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真正零成本好洗好用<br />\n對家仲要保證全力配合<br />\n我開始鐘意左限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6aa9bc53ac45d9f9f751c302fe30c4c14853eb1","tid":1997141,"uid":26876,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"黑警闖商場<br />\n商戶受重傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c61eb2d4505933922d8d8fdbe8568d2e08c62a","tid":1997141,"uid":19842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:36:26.000Z","msg":"日日都話有活動 班黑社會就日日哂馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5143fb305549da61de7df7dbdf229ae6745b7b12","tid":1997141,"uid":186181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"唔明就算罰2000蚊佢地好似執到金咁做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a704b0fe7c9198a5e8d00ab6e17e9b5f38b2e698","tid":1997141,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"d popo 黎埋捉人超過4個人前，開定手機錄片，話自己一個在場，附近既人都唔識，有無助上訴<br />\n<br />\n依家乜柒都佢講曬 佢話有就有咁撚惡？黑社會阿依家？"},{"pid":"f47af56274ffe1ac3d40570fd8b6a4b3c5fde68a","tid":1997141,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:38:19.000Z",